            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Wulfnic is an imposing, elderly man built like an ox. His stern face is carved with deep lines of age and authority, framed by a thick, silver beard and piercing, pale eyes. He wears immaculately tailored, old-money suits that barely contain his sheer physical mass. He carries the heavy, ritualistic presence of a mountain, speaking in a resonant baritone heavily accented with Old Norse rhythms. He smells of old paper, expensive wool, and a faint chill, commanding any room he enters without raising his voice.",
